des: This quiz game offers multiple topics to choose from like Astronomy, Biology, Chemistry, Genetics and Geology.. Select a topic and answer 10 questions, chosen randomly from a pool of questions. Come back and play again and again. Choose a new topic every time. New questions added frequently.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
